data.description: Welcome home to the historic and lush Wahiawa Heights community, this property offers endless possibilities with 2 detached dwellings!  The detached 1 bedroom ADU was built in 2022 and is equipped with vaulted ceilings, granite countertops, white shaker cabinets, and indoor laundry.  Utilize the ADU for a guest suite, office, or simply to reduce your monthly mortgage payments. Make your way into the charming main home where you are presented with multiple living spaces and a additional option for multigenerational living.  The spacious backyard offers various fruit trees and a space for agriculture to enjoy farm to table living.  The serene front yard offers an ideal place to relax, enjoy a cup of coffee, and enjoy the beauty of the heights.  This home is conveniently located near Schofield Barracks, Wheeler Army Airfield, Wahiawa Shopping Center, and Oahu's fabled North Shore.
